text: @Jacob_Rees_Mogg Another Tory MP defending the law breaking of Dominic Cummings-driving across the country spreading coronavirus when the law said he should have been self-isolating at HOME. Jacob, do you feel there is one law for us plebs and one for you, our rightful masters?
